Two-dimensional world
is about positivity.

72
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,470
But it's not a right timing.

73
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:11,140
Tomorrow is the premiere
of Book of Luo He God.

74
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:13,390
What if Mr Zhou Chuan's readers
couldn't get in

75
00:04:13,390 --> 00:04:14,470
if they want to buy his book?

76
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:16,910
Didn't you say you want to
sign his new book over?

77
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:19,500
