Mr Liang, don't joke on me.

92
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:48,790
In comparison to here,

93
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,830
Yuan Yue Publishing House's booth

94
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,670
is like a market.

95
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:53,350
Mr Xia went to receive

96
00:04:53,350 --> 00:04:54,110
his friends.

97
00:04:54,110 --> 00:04:56,030
He asked me to communicate with you.

98
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:57,070
When can the booth of

99
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:59,710
Yuan Yue Publishing House
turn from Comic-Con to a book fair?

100
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:05,430
Hello.

101
00:05:06,230 --> 00:05:07,070
Mr Yang.

102
00:05:07,590 --> 00:05:08,630
Yes.

103
00:05:09,110 --> 00:05:10,310
Rest assured.

104
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:12,630
I've been discussing
about the cosplaying.

105
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,300
Right, no problem.

106
00:05:15,110 --> 00:05:17,150
They will keep an eye on it.

107
00:05:17,150 --> 00:05:18,030
Right!

108
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,070
Okay, leave it to me.

109
00:05:20,070 --> 00:05:20,990
Goodbye.

110
00:05:22,550 --> 00:05:23,710
Have you listened it?

111
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:27,270
Hiring the cosplayer is an exemption
which is granted by Director Yang.

112
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,510
Please pass the message to Mr Xia.

113
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,870
The role-playing platform will be

114
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,270
lasted until the end.

115
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:37,470
As for Book of Luo He God,

116
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:40,190
we'll open two more passageways by then.

117
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:42,710
And hire someone to maintain the order.

118
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:44,390
What's big deal?

119
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,540
Everything is under my control.

120
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,030
But this...

121
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:49,670
Okay, just stop.

122
00:05:49,670 --> 00:05:50,870
It's useless to speak much.

123
00:05:51,470 --> 00:05:52,550
Let's go.

124
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:21,830
Gu Bai Zhi, why is it you?

125
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:23,230
You can't just drop by

126
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,940
even if we live nearby.

127
00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:26,630
Open the door,
I have something to tell you.

128
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:33,030
What is it?

129
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:36,550
Are you busy writing Huang Quan Inn?

130
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:38,150
It's a mess on your Weibo.

131
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:39,140
Don't you know that?

132
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,550
Weibo?

133
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,150
What's going on?

134
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,630
Yuan Yue Publishing House is outrageous.

135
00:06:50,909 --> 00:06:52,310
It's not enough for just one cosplayer.

136
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,710
Tomorrow is the launch day
of Book of Luo He God.

137
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:55,030
Yet they still wanted to hire
two more cosplayers.

138
00:06:56,230 --> 00:06:57,110
But your little editor

139
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:58,710
really worked hard for you.

140
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:01,750
She went up

141
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:03,110
against them

142
00:07:03,110 --> 00:07:04,909
just for your display board.

143
00:07:06,710 --> 00:07:08,870
What's going on?

144
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:12,470
Why are you coming to me?

145
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:15,190
Tomorrow night,

146
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:16,750
Xin Dun Books prepares

147
00:07:18,230 --> 00:07:19,630
a banquet to welcome Maurer.

148
00:07:19,990 --> 00:07:22,500
I'm here to invite you to the banquet.

149
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,230
I'm sorry.

150
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:26,780
I'm not planning to sign

151
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:29,790
the serial rights of Huang Quan Inn
over to Xin Dun Books.

152
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:31,990
Don't tell me you're going to sign it
over to Yuan Yue Publishing House.

153
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:37,390
Er Gou, I'm back.

154
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:39,830
I'm back.

155
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:46,380
You're back?

156
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:48,350
I...

157
00:07:48,350 --> 00:07:50,110
I... I mean,

158
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:53,190
Mr Zhou Chuan, I'm back to bother you.

159
00:07:54,990 --> 00:07:58,030
These are the stuffs
that you asked me to buy.

160
00:07:58,030 --> 00:08:00,340
You guys continue. I'm going.

161
00:08:02,590 --> 00:08:03,980
Your relationship
with this little editor...

162
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:16,470
Is not that simple.

163
00:08:25,710 --> 00:08:27,110
There's someone in the house.

164
00:08:27,110 --> 00:08:27,790
I'd better walk around

165
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:28,990
for a while before I go back.

166
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:29,790
Are you planning to

167
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:30,310
stay out for

168
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:31,510
two hours if she was
to stay that long?

169
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,990
Two hours?

170
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:34,710
Why does she want to stay that long?

171
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:35,670
Is she

172
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:37,630
going to stay for supper?

173
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:39,070
That was just a metaphor.

174
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:40,110
Do you know metaphor?

175
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:44,140
I think I should
find a place where I can sit

176
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,460
then I'll go back after a while.

177
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,429
Just send me a message

178
00:08:46,429 --> 00:08:47,630
after Director Gu has left.

179
00:08:48,309 --> 00:08:50,270
She lives nearby.

180
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,710
You guys will meet someday.

181
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:52,590
How many times do you plan to hide?

182
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,830
I'll hide every time I see her.

183
00:08:57,830 --> 00:08:58,750
It's unnecessary.

184
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,350
It's like we're cheating.

185
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:03,390
Mr Zhou Chuan, slow down.

186
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:04,620
I don't want to go in.

187
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,390
Hello, Director Gu.

188
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:16,390
What a coincidence. We meet again.

189
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:19,190
Both of you...

190
00:09:19,190 --> 00:09:20,900
She is now my tenant

191
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:22,070
and I'm her landlord.

192
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,540
Right.

193
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,670
I rented Mr Zhou Chuan's second floor.

194
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:28,070
Mr Zhou Chuan is a nice person.
He knew I'm homeless

195
00:09:28,070 --> 00:09:28,910
so...

196
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,030
I'm not going to hide it

197
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,430
since you've seen us.

198
00:09:32,830 --> 00:09:34,190
But I hope that
you could keep it as secret.

199
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:36,630
A man and a woman
lives in the same house.

200
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,910
It's hard for people not
to have impure thoughts.

201
00:09:39,350 --> 00:09:40,380
And you'll get affected

202
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:41,550
if your readers know it.

203
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:45,350
I don't mind.

204
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:46,750
I think

205
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,950
it will affect Chu Li's reputation

206
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:49,390
if this gets out

207
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:50,590
since she is a lady.

208
00:09:54,590 --> 00:09:56,220
Then I'll let you two be.

209
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:57,220
Just send me

210
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:59,070
a message if you want to go.

211
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:04,790
I'll leave first.

212
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:14,550
If you want to go?

213
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:15,700
Where do you want to go?

214
00:10:17,110 --> 00:10:18,590
She invited me to meet Maurer.

215
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:26,230
I think she's trying to get
Huang Quan Inn's serial rights.

216
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:31,150
I finally finished writing Huang Quan Inn.

217
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:36,190
Why is my shoulder this sore?

218
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,790
Dear Mr Zhou Chuan,

219
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,900
when can we sign the contract?

220
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:42,710
Tomorrow after the book fair,

221
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,390
bring the contract with you.

222
00:10:44,990 --> 00:10:45,830
Rest assured.

223
00:10:45,830 --> 00:10:48,910
I'll try my best to complete the mission.

224
00:10:55,190 --> 00:10:56,230
Be gentle.

225
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:57,870
Are you trying to break a rock?

226
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:07,510
Hello, Chief Editor Yu.

227
00:11:08,070 --> 00:11:09,070
I'm fine.

228
00:11:09,950 --> 00:11:11,670
Okay, I'll be right there.

229
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:13,550
Qiu Qiu is sick, you don't have to go.

230
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,340
I'll report it to you at night.

231
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,750
You just came back.
Are you going to

232
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:20,950
the editorial department
at this late hour?

233
00:11:23,110 --> 00:11:23,820
It's nothing.

234
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:25,460
Something urgent has come up
in the editorial department.

235
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:27,150
Just order the delivery
if you're hungry.

236
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:27,950
I'll leave first.

237
00:11:27,950 --> 00:11:28,830
I...

238
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:39,710
How about this?

239
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:41,590
Let's meet

240
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:42,790
each other halfway.

241
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:47,350
The editorial department
already compromised.

242
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:48,870
We just ask to suspend tomorrow's

243
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,390
comic exhibition for one day.

244
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,660
Tomorrow is the national

245
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:53,350
launch day of
Book of Luo He God with limited copies.

246
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:55,390
Based on the minimum of
respect for the author,

247
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,630
shouldn't the unrelated activities

248
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:58,030
be suspended?

249
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,990
Is there a conflict
between these two activities?

250
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,390
Why are you

251
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:03,100
putting all eggs in one basket?

252
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:04,510
Mr Xia,

253
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:06,550
I think this is a win-win situation.

254
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:08,510
Mr Liang,

255
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:10,310
do you know that tomorrow,

256
00:12:10,310 --> 00:12:12,470
Xin Dun Books has invited
world-renowned author

257
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:14,350
and director, Maurer over?

258
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:15,470
At this point, Yuan Yue

259
00:12:15,470 --> 00:12:16,790
is still not focusing

260
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:18,230
on Mr Zhou Chuan

261
00:12:18,230 --> 00:12:20,750
but to hire some cosplayers
and hold Comic-Con.

262
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:22,430
Aren't the priorities being misplaced?

263
00:12:22,430 --> 00:12:24,910
Right, I've misplaced the priorities.

264
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:25,950
Okay.

265
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:26,830
Hitting two millions copies

266
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,350
in three days,

267
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:29,620
you do it.

268
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:33,430
I'm from the editorial department,

269
00:12:33,430 --> 00:12:34,990
not the circulation department.

270
00:12:34,990 --> 00:12:37,150
I don't know much about these things.

271
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:39,830
But I know the practical realization
of the win-win situation

272
00:12:39,830 --> 00:12:42,550
is to maximize the sales
in the book fair under the premise

273
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:44,350
of protecting the author.

274
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:46,630
You can search for
Mr Zhou Chuan's Weibo.

275
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:48,070
The readers of Mr Zhou Chuan

276
00:12:48,070 --> 00:12:50,230
are dissatisfied with
Yuan Yue Publishing House now.

277
00:12:50,230 --> 00:12:52,150
Mr Zhou Chuan always
cherishes his readers.

278
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:54,430
This situation is no good for us.

279
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:58,550
I'm impressed.

280
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:01,230
Mr Xia,

281
