00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,870
He might be fifty minutes late.

566
00:24:20,870 --> 00:24:22,310
Fifty minutes more?

567
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:25,590
But

568
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:27,590
there's no connection between

569
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,390
the end time of the book selling
and photograph events

570
00:24:29,390 --> 00:24:31,550
and Mr Zhou Chuan's arrival time.

571
00:24:31,550 --> 00:24:33,790
Right, I didn't say so.

572
00:24:33,790 --> 00:24:34,750
Are you hungry?

573
00:24:37,190 --> 00:24:37,860
I am.

574
00:24:38,070 --> 00:24:38,870
Let's go eat.

575
00:24:38,870 --> 00:24:39,990
Let's go. Let's go and eat.

576
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:40,820
Do you want to join us?

577
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:47,150
Chief Editor Yu,

578
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:50,390
why do I have a bad feeling?

579
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:54,760
[Reading makes the life better.]

580
00:24:55,550 --> 00:24:56,870
Really?

581
00:24:56,870 --> 00:24:58,660
The animation photograph is ongoing?

582
00:24:58,660 --> 00:25:00,750
Shouldn't they hold the limited
launch for Zhou Chuan?

583
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,430
Right, the book selling
and photograph event

584
00:25:02,430 --> 00:25:04,190
should be ended at noon.

585
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:05,910
But there's a steady stream

586
00:25:05,910 --> 00:25:06,630
of anime fans now.

587
00:25:06,630 --> 00:25:07,590
What's wrong with Yuan Yue
Publishing House? Look at the time.

588
00:25:07,590 --> 00:25:08,780
Liang Chong Lang,

589
00:25:08,780 --> 00:25:10,670
he went mad to boost their sales.

590
00:25:10,670 --> 00:25:11,670
We haven't purchased it!

591
00:25:11,670 --> 00:25:12,390
Right!

592
00:25:12,390 --> 00:25:14,270
There're many people in the Comic-Con!
Look at the time!

593
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:15,060
Start it quickly!

594
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:16,310
Hurry up! We have things to do too!

595
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:17,310
When is he coming? When?

596
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:18,390
We have limited time!

597
00:25:18,390 --> 00:25:19,630
We've waited for so long, hurry up!

598
00:25:19,630 --> 00:25:20,670
Geez!

599
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:22,150
Chief Editor Yu,

600
00:25:22,750 --> 00:25:23,420
what's going on?

601
00:25:23,420 --> 00:25:24,790
It's already twenty past twelve.

602
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:26,110
Why are they still allowing

603
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:27,380
the people to enter?

604
00:25:27,380 --> 00:25:28,950
When can they clear the place?

605
00:25:31,910 --> 00:25:33,470
Chief Editor Yu,

606
00:25:33,470 --> 00:25:35,430
the lunch is ready.
Why don't we just eat first?

607
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:37,750
Who has the mood to eat now?

608
00:25:38,990 --> 00:25:41,390
The members of circulation department
are enjoying their lunch.

609
00:25:41,390 --> 00:25:42,550
Where are they?

610
00:25:43,340 --> 00:25:44,270
Over there.

611
00:25:44,950 --> 00:25:46,300
Ah Xiang, you stay here as lookout.

612
00:25:46,300 --> 00:25:47,510
Let's go there.

613
00:25:52,110 --> 00:25:53,390
Look, look, look.

614
00:25:53,390 --> 00:25:54,550
We're old.

615
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:58,350
I see you two enjoying your meal.

616
00:25:58,910 --> 00:26:00,110
You want some?

617
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:00,990
Mr Liang,

618
00:26:01,380 --> 00:26:02,700
I've told you once.

619
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:05,110
I'm not saying it again.

620
00:26:05,110 --> 00:26:06,150
You had agreed to

621
00:26:06,150 --> 00:26:07,590
end the events before twelve.

622
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:08,510
Look at the time now.

623
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:10,300
Why haven't you controlled the stream?

624
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:12,030
Zhou Chuan hasn't reached too.

625
00:26:12,030 --> 00:26:13,380
Isn't he stuck in the traffic?

626
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:15,950
Just one more hour,
Director Yang already agreed.

627
00:26:17,430 --> 00:26:18,510
Chief Editor Yu,

628
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:21,270
we didn't expect

629
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:22,870
the role-playing enthusiasts

630
00:26:22,870 --> 00:26:23,390
would be this much.

631
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:24,070
Right.

632
00:26:24,070 --> 00:26:25,310
And there are many people

633
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:27,870
coming from distant places.

634
00:26:28,390 --> 00:26:31,470
They are here to support us.

635
00:26:31,470 --> 00:26:32,830
We can't disappoint them

636
00:26:32,830 --> 00:26:33,910
and ask them leave just like this.

637
00:26:33,910 --> 00:26:34,790
Right.

638
00:26:34,790 --> 00:26:36,030
Then have you thought about this?

639
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:37,700
What if Zhou Chuan's
fans couldn't enter

640
00:26:37,700 --> 00:26:38,790
and purchase the book?

641
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:41,100
But I didn't see

642
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:42,510
any of them making a fuss

643
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:43,670
but you.

644
00:26:43,670 --> 00:26:45,060
What's the big deal?

645
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:46,820
Why are you making this difficult?

646
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:49,390
So, you act like nothing happened

647
00:26:49,390 --> 00:26:51,270
because they didn't
make a fuss in front of you?

648
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:53,710
Why did you break your promise
and extend the time?

649
00:26:53,710 --> 00:26:55,710
Or do you think Zhou Chuan's readers

650
00:26:55,710 --> 00:26:57,110
will come to buy
the books no matter what

651
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:59,030
since they've bought
the admission tickets?

652
00:26:59,030 --> 00:27:00,390
So, it doesn't matter to
keep them waiting,

653
00:27:00,390 --> 00:27:01,630
right?

654
00:27:01,630 --> 00:27:03,220
Do you show respect to the author

655
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:04,150
and the readers?

656
00:27:04,150 --> 00:27:05,950
Then do you show respect to the leader

657
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:07,390
and the superior?

658
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:08,990
Who is he?

659
00:27:10,190 --> 00:27:11,150
He is your superior

660
00:27:11,150 --> 00:27:12,140
not your grandson.

661
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:13,310
What makes you think

662
00:27:13,310 --> 00:27:14,470
you can teach him?

663
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:15,630
Who do you think you are?

664
00:27:16,870 --> 00:27:18,670
Respect the author?

665
00:27:18,670 --> 00:27:20,350
Respect the readers?

666
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:21,590
That's so kind of you.

667
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:22,950
Don't be an editor,

668
00:27:22,950 --> 00:27:24,310
go start a charity!

669
00:27:24,710 --> 00:27:27,590
You just implement
the leader's decision,

670
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:29,510
you have no right to
tell us what to do!

671
00:27:35,990 --> 00:27:37,470
Hello, Mr Zhou Chuan.

672
00:27:37,830 --> 00:27:39,310
You've reached?

673
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:41,270
Okay, I'll come pick you up.

674
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:44,270
Didn't you say he
needs fifty minutes more?

675
00:27:44,820 --> 00:27:45,580
But he got here early.

676
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:47,190
There's nothing I can do.

677
00:27:47,190 --> 00:27:48,340
Chief Editor, I'm going to pick him up.

678
00:27:48,340 --> 00:27:49,220
Okay.

679
00:27:58,390 --> 00:27:59,150
Then I'll stop eating.

680
00:27:59,150 --> 00:28:00,340
I'll go and manage the situation first.

681
00:28:08,570 --> 00:28:09,990
[What's wrong with
Yuan Yue Publishing House?]

682
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,600
[Isn't Book of Luo He God
start at twelve o'clock?]

683
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:14,120
[Why are they still letting
the COSER enthusiasts in?]

684
00:28:18,310 --> 00:28:19,990
My Weibo is going to explode.

685
00:28:19,990 --> 00:28:21,230
What's the situation up there?

686
00:28:21,230 --> 00:28:22,710
The circulation department
finally started

687
00:28:22,710 --> 00:28:24,230
to manage the situation
as they heard you've reached.

688
00:28:24,230 --> 00:28:25,270
Let's go quickly.

689
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:26,070
Let's go.

690
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:29,990
Hello.

691
00:28:30,310 --> 00:28:32,030
[It's me, Mr Liang.]

692
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:33,630
Chu Li, listen to me.

693
00:28:33,630 --> 00:28:35,350
You do whatever it takes to

694
00:28:35,350 --> 00:28:36,310
hold Zhou Chuan off.

695
00:28:36,310 --> 00:28:37,230
[At least ten minutes.]

696
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:38,150
[Do you understand?]

697
00:28:38,470 --> 00:28:39,430
Mr Liang,

698
00:28:39,430 --> 00:28:41,350
Mr Zhou Chuan has entered the venue.

699
00:28:41,350 --> 00:28:42,310
[He has entered?]

700
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:44,630
This is not right.

701
00:28:45,470 --> 00:28:46,510
Young lady,

702
00:28:46,990 --> 00:28:48,390
why is it so quiet

703
00:28:48,390 --> 00:28:50,110
if you've entered the venue?

704
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:51,870
[Is this some kind of a trick?]

705
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:53,350
[I warn you.]

706
00:28:53,910 --> 00:28:56,790
Are you trying to get back at me?

707
00:28:56,790 --> 00:28:57,870
I tell you.

708
00:28:57,870 --> 00:28:59,350
If you don't hold Zhou Chuan off,

709
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:01,350
[you don't have to come back to
Yuan Yue Publishing House.]

710
00:29:03,230 --> 00:29:04,380
You...

711
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:07,670
I am Zhou Chuan.

712
00:29:08,470 --> 00:29:10,470
What's wrong with
Yuan Yue Publishing House?

713
00:29:10,470 --> 00:29:12,710
[You're still letting the
role-playing enthusiasts in now.]

714
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:14,310
Isn't the event
supposed to end at twelve?

715
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:16,150
Who are they trying to take photo with?

716
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:17,140
Is it me?

717
00:29:17,140 --> 00:29:18,830
Mr Zhou Chuan, calm down.

718
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:19,630
Listen to me.

719
00:29:19,630 --> 00:29:20,990
[How can I not be agitated?]

720
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:23,110
There are many comments on my Weibo.

721
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:24,670
They are all my fans' complaints.

722
00:29:24,670 --> 00:29:25,710
Others' fans are more

723
00:29:25,710 --> 00:29:27,310
important than mine, right?

724
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,870
What's the matter
with the circulation department?

725
00:29:29,870 --> 00:29:31,590
[Just quit if you don't
want to sell the books.]

726
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:32,660
Just hold a clearance sale

727
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:33,540
in the farmers' market,

728
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:34,950
such as ten dollars for three catties.

729
00:29:34,950 --> 00:29:36,620
I'm sure it's more lively than now.

730
00:29:36,620 --> 00:29:38,750
Mr Zhou Chuan, okay, I admit

731
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:40,190
that the current situation

732
00:29:40,190 --> 00:29:42,070
makes you mad.

733
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:43,590
[But you can rest assured.]

734
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:45,070
[Everything]

735
00:29:45,070 --> 00:29:46,110
can...

736
00:29:46,950 --> 00:29:47,870
Hello.

737
00:29:53,070 --> 00:29:54,750
I came out at ten thirty.

738
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:56,470
How would I know
there'll be a traffic jam?

739
00:29:56,710 --> 00:29:57,860
I haven't had my breakfast too.

740
00:29:57,860 --> 00:29:59,470
What are you trying to say?

741
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:01,790
I didn't mean to be late.

742
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:03,870
I didn't know
there'll be a traffic accident.

743
00:30:04,510 --> 00:30:05,750
I've tried to reach here as fast as I can.

744
00:30:06,150 --> 00:30:07,670
Why are you telling me this?

745
00:30:07,670 --> 00:30:08,590
I...

746
00:30:10,830 --> 00:30:12,790
I'm afraid you'll start a fight
with the circulation department.

747
00:30:12,790 --> 00:30:13,700
You might be

748
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:15,020
a dead meat when I reach

749
00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:17,070
and come back to haunt me, asking me

750
00:30:17,070 --> 00:30:19,350
why I didn't protect you.

751
00:30:20,630 --> 00:30:21,670
The book fair is crowded.

752
00:30:21,670 --> 00:30:23,820
I know you hate to go
to the crowded place.

753
00:30:23,820 --> 00:30:25,830
So, I'm touched that you came.

754
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:27,230
My fans say

755
00:30:27,230 --> 00:30:28,340
they wouldn't buy a book

756
00:30:28,340 --> 00:30:30,630
from Yuan Yue Publishing House
if it wasn't for me.

757
00:30:31,990 --> 00:30:32,830
Do you regret?

758
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,270
About what?

759
00:30:34,270 --> 00:30:35,790
About choosing
Yuan Yue Publishing House.

760
00:30:37,390 --> 00:30:40,630
There are tiresome
circulation departments,

761
00:30:40,630 --> 00:30:41,870
illustrators who are hard to communicate,

762
00:30:41,870 --> 00:30:43,110
and infuriating authors everywhere.

763
00:30:43,110 --> 00:30:44,590
So, I regret nothing.

764
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:45,990
Let's go.

765
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:48,190
Let's go.

766
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:55,270
Excuse me! Excuse me!

767
00:31:15,390 --> 00:31:17,630
That should be Maurer.

768
00:31:17,630 --> 00:31:19,670
His book signing is going to
start at three o'clock.

769
00:31:19,670 --> 00:31:20,550
Mr Zhou Chuan,

770
00:31:20,550 --> 00:31:22,470
don't tell me you are starstruck.

771
00:31:23,270 --> 00:31:24,390
Of course not.

772
00:31:24,390 --> 00:31:26,030
I can have dinner with him tonight.

773
00:31:26,870 --> 00:31:29,110
Luckily, you didn't lose your mind.

774
00:31:37,470 --> 00:31:39,470
They sweep it all real quick.

775
00:31:39,470 --> 00:31:40,790
It's only been five minutes

776
00:31:41,150 --> 00:31:42,060
and they are done?

777
00:31:43,430 --> 00:31:46,390
I guess the circulation department
went all out.

778
00:31:52,670 --> 00:31:53,670
Mr Zhou Chuan!

779
00:31:54,670 --> 00:31:55,670
Mr Zhou Chuan!

780
00:31:55,950 --> 00:31:56,790
You're here.

781
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:57,580
Mr Liang

782
00:31:58,190 --> 00:32:00,220
is waiting for you at the rest room.

783
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:01,070
Miao,

784
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:02,950
I'll mistake you as the member of

785
00:32:02,950 --> 00:32:04,830
the circulation department
if I didn't know you're an editor.

786
00:32:06,670 --> 00:32:07,950
We are all

787
00:32:08,390 --> 00:32:09,790
from Yuan Yue Publishing House

788
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:11,670
and also the leaders
of Yuan Yue Publishing House.

789
00:32:11,670 --> 00:32:13,420
There's no discrimination.

790
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:14,950
Old workers like us

791
00:32:15,390 --> 00:32:16,830
are no match to the youngsters.

792
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:18,030
They have short temper.

793
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,230
We are just doing our jobs.

794
00:32:19,230 --> 00:32:19,990
We'll just do

795
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:21,390
as the leaders told us to

796
00:32:21,390 --> 00:32:23,510
no matter what position we hold.

797
00:32:23,510 --> 00:32:24,980
Okay. Then,

798
00:32:25,510 --> 00:32:27,470
I'll stop bothering you.

799
00:32:27,910 --> 00:32:29,550
Chu Li, take me there.

800
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:31,630
This way, please.

801
00:32:40,820 --> 00:32:42,510
Director Gu, are you all right?

802
00:32:43,350 --> 00:32:45,310
You haven't rested these few days

803
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,070
to arrange

804
00:32:46,070 --> 00:32:47,870
this event for Maurer.

805
00:32:47,870 --> 00:32:49,510
And you've been standing for so long.

806
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:51,630
Why don't you go and
rest in the small room?

807
00:32:52,270 --> 00:32:54,110
I'm fine. It's going to end soon.

808
00:32:54,910 --> 00:32:56,510
I have to keep an eye on the event.

809
00:32:58,980 --> 00:32:59,590
Thank you.

810
00:32:59,590 --> 00:33:00,470
You're welcome.

811
00:33:05,670 --> 00:33:06,870
Mr Zhou Chuan,

812
00:33:06,870 --> 00:33:07,900
you've finally reached.

813
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:09,470
You must be tired. Have a seat.

814
00:33:09,470 --> 00:33:11,230
You haven't eaten yet, right?
Let's eat first.

815
00:33:11,230 --> 00:33:12,180
I'm not tired.

816
00:33:12,180 --> 00:33:14,390
It's no match to
the circulation department.

817
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:16,310
That's our job.

818
00:33:16,310 --> 00:33:18,310
Here. Eat it.

819
00:33:20,790 --> 00:33:21,390
Drink some water.

820
00:33:22,990 --> 00:33:23,710
Chu Li,

821
00:33:24,110 --> 00:33:25,230
it's quite busy out there.

822
00:33:25,230 --> 00:33:26,910
Go and help them.

823
00:33:29,070 --> 00:33:30,270
Have you not eaten yet?

824
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:31,790
Here, eat it first.

825
00:33:32,350 --> 00:33:33,310
Never mind, you eat it.

826
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:34,300
I'll go and help them.

827
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:35,740
Chu Li,

828
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:39,580
Mr Zhou Chuan has said it.

829
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:40,670
He shows you consideration.

830
00:33:40,670 --> 00:33:41,340
Just eat it.

831
00:33:43,470 --> 00:33:44,150
Here.

832
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:45,270
Sit here.

833
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:48,630
Thank you, Mr Zhou Chuan.

834
00:33:51,870 --> 00:33:53,220
Mr Zhou Chuan, come sit here.

835
00:33:53,220 --> 00:33:54,710
Here, sit.

836
00:33:55,230 --> 00:33:56,630
You must be tired.

837
00:33:56,630 --> 00:33:58,910
Everyone understands
you were stuck in the traffic.

838
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:00,550
Look.

839
00:34:01,030 --> 00:34:02,190
I'm sorry.

840
00:34:02,190 --> 00:34:04,190
You saw the strong reaction

841
00:34:04,190 --> 00:34:06,470
of the role-playing enthusiasts
out there too.

842
00:34:06,990 --> 00:34:08,230
I had no choice

843
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:10,430
but to extend an hour

